Boom, added news functionality. Just pass what you want me to use as a search query (as a city parameter) and what type of news you want (options are rt_Business, rt_Entertainment, rt_Health, rt_Politics, rt_Sports, rt_US, rt_World, and rt_ScienceAndTechnology). The first paramater has to be "city" and the second has to be "newsType". Post this to /api/getNews and a json result will be returned.
